in a private residence.)

180
00:08:40,930 --> 00:08:43,270
(The police are currently investigating.)

181
00:08:46,090 --> 00:08:47,390
Well? Did you get a shot?

182
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:48,470
Officer Yao.

183
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,390
How's everything inside?

184
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:52,870
First, let me introduce
our newest member, Liu Weitao.

185
00:08:53,810 --> 00:08:54,479
Officer Yao.

186
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,350
I know you.

187
00:08:57,760 --> 00:08:59,689
Officer Yao, based on
our initial investigations,

188
00:08:59,690 --> 00:09:00,569
the victim and his pet dog

189
00:09:00,570 --> 00:09:01,710
died from stab wounds.

190
00:09:01,930 --> 00:09:04,110
There are signs of a brawl inside.
No weapon has been found.

191
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:08,820
The victim is Deng Rongtian,

192
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,020
nicknamed Black Guy Tian.

193
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:11,760
He's the boss of Luen Kee,
a triad gang based in Jordan.

194
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:12,540
He was a good fighter,

195
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,470
and built his fortune
through real estate.

196
00:09:14,470 --> 00:09:16,520
He's also involved in prostitution,
gambling, drugs, the whole lot.

197
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,300
Want to puke?

198
00:09:22,810 --> 00:09:23,710
Swallow it.

199
00:09:25,570 --> 00:09:26,870
Swallow it!

200
00:09:27,170 --> 00:09:29,230
I told you, the canteen
has been serving rotten food.

201
00:09:29,410 --> 00:09:30,809
Puke outside, go!

202
00:09:30,810 --> 00:09:31,540
Stop.

203
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,969
Reporters are gathered outside.

204
00:09:33,970 --> 00:09:35,300
You want to be on the news

205
00:09:35,450 --> 00:09:36,820
and embarrass the police force?

206
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,590
Give me your hand.

207
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,630
Press here.

208
00:09:41,690 --> 00:09:43,660
It's a meridian spot that can
stop you from vomiting.

209
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,020
Thank you, sir.

210
00:09:47,290 --> 00:09:48,540
Thank him.

211
00:09:51,210 --> 00:09:52,630
This guy has lots of enemies.

212
00:09:53,170 --> 00:09:53,929
How about this?

213
00:09:53,930 --> 00:09:55,390
I'll ask the Anti-triad Squad

214
00:09:55,450 --> 00:09:56,820
and see which of his enemies did this.

215
00:09:58,210 --> 00:09:59,300
I don't think an enemy did this.

216
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,870
He was literally slaughtered.

217
00:10:01,570 --> 00:10:02,750
They slashed his aorta

218
00:10:02,970 --> 00:10:04,300
and let him bleed to death.

219
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,540
Officer Yao.

220
00:10:21,450 --> 00:10:22,660
You, sit there.

221
00:10:23,930 --> 00:10:24,660
Weitao.

222
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:25,710
Officer Yao.

223
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:27,270
Interrogate them separately.

224
00:10:27,290 --> 00:10:27,929
Bring her there.

225
00:10:27,930 --> 00:10:29,929
Officer, where are we going?

226
00:10:29,930 --> 00:10:30,820
I don't know.

227
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:31,879
What do you mean?

228
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:32,969
I asked for your name.

229
00:10:32,970 --> 00:10:35,140
"I" is my first name,
"Don't Know" is my last name.

230
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,900
I'm warning you, don't try to be funny!

231
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:37,990
Officer.

232
00:10:38,090 --> 00:10:40,169
Your name's Lin Minzhi?
Let's have dinner together later.

233
00:10:40,170 --> 00:10:41,020
That's enough!

234
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:43,820
Put your leg down.

235
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,750
I said, put your leg down.

236
00:10:48,690 --> 00:10:49,870
Is it that sunny here?

237
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:51,180
What's with the sunglasses indoors?

238
00:10:51,210 --> 00:10:52,329
Officer, I'm blind.

239
00:10:52,330 --> 00:10:53,590
I can't see without my sunglasses.

240
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,990
You must be on drugs.

241
00:10:55,090 --> 00:10:56,660
You can't even open your eyes.

242
00:10:57,210 --> 00:10:58,990
Take him to the washroom
and do a urine test.

243
00:10:59,290 --> 00:11:00,350
Roger that.

244
00:11:00,570 --> 00:11:01,470
Get up.

245
00:11:06,690 --> 00:11:07,470
Come in.

246
00:11:12,970 --> 00:11:14,590
Black Guy Tian's report is out.

247
00:11:14,970 --> 00:11:16,020
Just as I expected.

248
00:11:16,810 --> 00:11:18,990
His aorta was slashed.
He died within a minute.

249
00:11:19,690 --> 00:11:21,020
Any clues from the Anti-triad Squad?

250
00:11:21,570 --> 00:11:22,820
He's got so many enemies.

251
00:11:23,290 --> 00:11:26,230
He's always been at loggerheads
with Woh Kee, another triad gang.

252
00:11:26,690 --> 00:11:28,120
Woh Kee has no reason
to kill him, though.

253
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,020
This method is too brutal.

254
00:11:30,110 --> 00:11:31,560
Doesn't look like
a typical triad revenge.

255
00:11:32,930 --> 00:11:34,780
If it's not a triad revenge,

256
00:11:35,570 --> 00:11:36,900
could it be

257
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,990
a burglary, then?

258
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,329
Maybe he saw the burglar,

259
00:11:40,330 --> 00:11:41,470
so they killed him.

260
00:11:41,570 --> 00:11:42,660
We searched his house

261
00:11:42,810 --> 00:11:44,089
and found HKD 200,000 in cash,

262
00:11:44,090 --> 00:11:44,999
plus four luxury watches.

263
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:45,990
Doesn't look like a burglary.

264
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,209
Interrogate his enemies

265
00:11:49,210 --> 00:11:50,359
and see if we can get any clues.

266
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,060
Roger that.

267
00:11:52,090 --> 00:11:52,870
Guangyao.

268
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:57,750
How many times have I told you?

269
00:11:57,970 --> 00:11:59,630
Show some restraint in your work.

270
00:12:00,090 --> 00:12:01,760
Last time, you beat the crap
out of that gangster,

271
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:03,110
