272
00:12:03,450 --> 00:12:04,049
Come on.

273
00:12:04,050 --> 00:12:05,140
You can solve that for me.

274
00:12:05,210 --> 00:12:06,289
This is the Crime Unit,

275
00:12:06,290 --> 00:12:07,590
